    "protected": false,
    "rendered": "<p>Explore an interesting observation on the Neighbour Discovery Protocol (NDP) in IPv6, in regard to Neighbour Solicitation and Advertisements.</p>\n<div class=\"more-link-wrapper\"><a class=\"more-link\" href=\"https://www.daryllswer.com/interesting-ipv6-observation-on-ndp-neighbour-discovery-protocol/\">Continue reading<span class=\"screen-reader-text\">Interesting IPv6 observation on NDP (Neighbour Discovery Protocol)</span></a></div>\n"
  },
